data.description: This beautiful ranch home is a must see! Tucked away on a cul-de-sac in the lovely Hidden Cove neighborhood, with a view of Hoffler Creek out front and a large, serene back yard. Features include a foyer, dining room, family room with hardwood floors and gas fireplace, eat-in kitchen, primary suite on one end and two additional bedrooms and full bathroom at the opposite end. Plus, a large finished room over the garage serving as the 4th bedroom. The spacious primary bedroom includes an ensuite with dual vanity and a walk-in closet. Conveniently located near shopping, military bases, and highways. Call today to schedule your private showing!
